La Soluce ComplŠte:
*******************
PadH0  = direction Haut Paddle0
PadB0  = direction Bas Paddle0
PadG0  = direction Gauche Paddle0
PadD0  = direction Droite Paddle0
Pause0 = Bouton de Pause Paddle0
Option0= Bouton Option Paddle0
